cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "WES: A Wang-Engel-Streck phenology framework for multi-stage winter wheat phenology prediction from satellite remote sensing"
message: "If you use this software in academic work, please cite both the software and the associated paper (when published)."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Mangidis
    given-names: Vlasis
    affiliation: "Department of Agronomy, Purdue University"
